{"tid":347470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今季流感死亡人數已超沙士","createTime":"2017-08-04T23:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T00:48:11.000Z","uid":89227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af0fc71e3f483320d771d737ab5797f773413e6d","tid":347470,"uid":89227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T23:40:11.000Z","msg":"沙士－死亡人數：299人（包括8名醫護人員）<br />\n<br />\n2017夏季流感－死亡的成年人衝破三百大關達三百零四名<br />\n<br />\n點解政府好似無咩反應咁，仲唔停工停課！？"},{"pid":"a8e0ac19064b7885b014aac49abfdb3430e859f3","tid":347470,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T23:41:54.000Z","msg":"死多幾件廢老仲好"},{"pid":"93720d53a64cce563ff461b4dfff4d65429f84be","tid":347470,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T23:45:34.000Z","msg":"假膠?<br />\n<br />\n沙士係精壯成年人都死流感唔係<br />\n2003年都肯定因為季候性流感死幾百人  年年都要面對冇計架wo"},{"pid":"9be199cce2ef5650e0481e9821b4d896ea24919b","tid":347470,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:22:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假膠?<br />\n<br />\n沙士係精壯成年人都死流感唔係<br />\n2003年都肯定因為季候性流感死幾百人  年年都要面對冇計架wo</blockquote><br />\nSARS都係死老弱架傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>不同年齡段的死亡率為：24歲和以下人群死亡率為1%，25到44歲死亡率為6%，45到64歲死亡率15%，65歲以上的死亡率則為100%。<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E6%80%A5%E6%80%A7%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E7%B6%9C%E5%90%88%E7%97%87&d=yJCRCZc3iqB%2Brp8iXfvYeQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=e6b81296\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症</a></em><br />\n<br />\n壯年有SARS死亡率都係好低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c52c9fd38f2beb46030fae8805ab46220213e55","tid":347470,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沙士－死亡人數：299人（包括8名醫護人員）<br />\n<br />\n2017夏季流感－死亡的成年人衝破三百大關達三百零四名<br />\n<br />\n點解政府好似無咩反應咁，仲唔停工停課！？</blockquote><br />\n因為政府唔想比樓市爆<br />\n如果唔係而家已經係SARS價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a1b7e8133f029a0c7d637b4144aa1ff04f87c3","tid":347470,"uid":6211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:47:11.000Z","msg":"睇多d新聞啦<br />\n年年流感都係死好多人"},{"pid":"310dc71ec3030124bef4722edd62370e2c76e66f","tid":347470,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>沙士－死亡人數：299人（包括8名醫護人員）<br />\n<br />\n2017夏季流感－死亡的成年人衝破三百大關達三百零四名<br />\n<br />\n點解政府好似無咩反應咁，仲唔停工停課！？</blockquote><br />\n因為政府唔想比樓市爆<br />\n如果唔係而家已經係SARS價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSARS撞正金融海嘯先有咁低價，而家市場維持極高購買力，跌唔夠半成就托返上去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}